<span id="freeTextContainer16529219174582545966">My husband loved this book and convinced me to order it from the UK (no sellers in the US). I am having a very hard time following the back and forth of this one between past and present. I&apos;m not sure if it&apos;s a translation issue or not since my husband read it in the original spanish and I&apos;m reading the translated english version. I&apos;m downgrading this to a 2 star but will soldier on and try to finish. Husband says it starts out very slow. I&apos;m half way through and it&apos;s still painfully slow.</span>
